  <text>
    <body>
<div type="act" n="5">
    <head>ACTE V.</head>
  <div type="scene" n="1">
    <head>SCENE PREMIERE.</head>
    <sp>
      <speaker>ANTIGONE</speaker>
      <stage type="stage-direction">
seule.       </stage>

<l n="1331">
A 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">Quoy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">Quoi </rdg>
      </app>
te resous-tu Princesse infortunée&#160;? </l>

<l n="1332">
Ta Mere vient de mourir dans tes bras, </l>

<l n="1333">
Ne sçaurois-tu 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">suivre </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">suiure </rdg>
      </app>
ses 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">pas </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">pas, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1334">
Et finir en mourant ta triste destinée&#160;? </l>

<l n="1335">
A de 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">nouveaux </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">nouueaux </rdg>
      </app>
mal-heurs te veux-tu 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">reserver&#160;? </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">reseruer&#160;? </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1336">
Tes 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Freres </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">freres </rdg>
      </app>
sont aux 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #C #D #E">mains, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B">maïns, </rdg>
      </app>
rien ne les peut 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">sauver </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">sauuer </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1337">
De leurs cruelles armes. </l>

<l n="1338">
Leur exemple t’anime à te percer le flanc, </l>

<l n="1339">
Et 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">toy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">toi </rdg>
      </app>
seule verses des larmes, </l>

<l n="1340">
Tous les autres versent du sang. </l>

<l n="1341">
Quelle est de mes mal-heurs 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">l’extrémité </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">l’extremité </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">mortelle, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #D">mortelle&#160;? </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#C">mortelle </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1342">
Où ma douleur doit-elle recourir&#160;? </l>

<l n="1343">
Dois-je 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#E">vivre, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">viure, </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">vivre&#160;? </rdg>
      </app>
dois-je mourir&#160;? </l>

<l n="1344">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">Un </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Vn </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">amant </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">Amant </rdg>
      </app>
me retient, 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">une </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">vne </rdg>
      </app>
Mere 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">m’apelle, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">m’appelle. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1345">
Dans la nuit du 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">tombeau, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">tombeau </rdg>
      </app>
je la 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">voy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">voi </rdg>
      </app>
qui m’attend, </l>

<l n="1346">
Ce que veut la raison, l’amour me le 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">défend </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">défend, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1347">
Et m’en oste 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">l’envie. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">l’enuie. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1348">
Que je 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">voy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">voi </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">vois </rdg>
      </app>
de sujets d’abandonner le jour&#160;! </l>

<l n="1349">
Mais helas&#160;! qu’on tient à la vie, </l>

<l n="1350">
Quand on tient si fort à l’amour&#160;! </l>

<l n="1351">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">Oüy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">Oüi </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">Ouy </rdg>
      </app>
tu retiens, Amour, mon ame 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">fugitive, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">fugitiue, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1352">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">Je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Ie </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">reconnoy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">reconnoi </rdg>
        <rdg wit="#D">reconnois </rdg>
      </app>
la voix de mon Vainqueur, </l>

<l n="1353">
L’esperance est morte en mon 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">cœur </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">cœur, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1354">
Et cependant tu vis, &amp; tu veux que 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">ie </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">vive. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">viue. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1355">
Tu dis que mon Amant me 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">suivroit </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">suiuroit </rdg>
      </app>
au tombeau, </l>

<l n="1356">
Que je dois de mes jours 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #E">conseruer </lem>
        <rdg wit="#B #C #D">conserver </rdg>
      </app>
le flambeau, </l>

<l n="1357">
Pour 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">sauver </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">sauuer </rdg>
      </app>
ce que j’aime. </l>

<l n="1358">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #C #E">Hemon </lem>
        <rdg wit="#D">Hémon, </rdg>
      </app>

      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #E">voy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C #D">voi </rdg>
      </app>
le 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">pouvoir </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">pouuoir </rdg>
      </app>
que l’amour a sur 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">moy, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">moi, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1359">

      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">Je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">Ie </rdg>
      </app>
ne ne 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">vivrois </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">viurois </rdg>
      </app>
pas pour 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">moy-mesme, </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">moi-mesme, </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1360">
Et 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">je </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">ie </rdg>
      </app>
veux bien 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">vivre </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">viure </rdg>
      </app>
pour 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">toy. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">toi. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

<l n="1361">
Si jamais tu doutas de ma flamme fidelle… </l>

<l n="1362">
Mais 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#A #B #D #E">voicy </lem>
        <rdg wit="#C">voici </rdg>
      </app>
du combat la funeste 
      <app>
        <lem wit="#B #C #D #E">nouvelle. </lem>
        <rdg wit="#A">nouuelle. </rdg>
      </app>
</l>

</sp>
</div>
</div>
